s galvanized pipes, electric resistance welding mild steel pipes, black pipes, structural pipes, solar structural pipes, square and round pipes, rectangular pipes, and pre-engineered buildings, as well as machinery. It also manufactures and sells agricultural equipment, such as groundnut de-stoner machines, potato digger and grader machines, pipe winder machines, reversible MB ploughs, rotavators, hydraulic post hole diggers, conicale fertilizer broadcasters, and portable generators with streetlights. In addition, the company offers fire protection systems comprising fire hydrant, fire pumping, sprinkler, gas suppression, water mist, automatic CO2 flooding, and high medium velocity water spray systems, as well as foam bladders; and fire detection systems, such as fire alarm systems, fire alarm detectors, and wireless fire detection and alarm systems. It sells its products to wholesalers and distributors through independent sales and distribution networks. The company serves various sectors, such as agriculture, oil, public health, housing, irrigation, engineering, infrastructural, and industrial, etc. Shree Marutinandan Tubes Limited was founded in 1993 and is based in Ahmedabad, India."}}